Image 1 of 5 showing our ray tracer can handle linear transformations.

This image is of a polygon shaped and colored like a gourd under a simple white directional light down the z-axis. 

Time to render: 2 minutes, 43 seconds.

We are using the gourd.obj file from the following resource: http://people.sc.fsu.edu/~jburkardt/data/obj/obj.html.